channel.title: Coder here: will code your server
channel.description:
I'm looking for someone to code for. Yes i actually know how to code. I know how to public voids, public booleans, int's, if.. else... and a bunch of other things.
What do you need. [hr] A source A client A brain msn Ability to host.
